data.description: Welcome to this stunning, fully remodeled 2-story home nestled atop a hill in the delightful Kingston Woods neighborhood! Experience the beauty of the open concept spacious adorning the main level. Step inside and be captivated by the brand new kitchen, complete with quartz countertop, modern stove and microwave, and updated appliances. The house has undergone a complete repaint, boasting gorgeous hardwood floors and lavishly remodeled bathrooms with high-end finishes. Not to mention, the landscaping has been revitalized with new plants and trees. The front porch has been tastefully redone, and the garage features easy-to-clean epoxy flooring. Conveniently situated in the Rocky Hill/Bearden community, this home is close to the best schools and shopping. The screened-in porch and fenced backyard make it a perfect haven for your family. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this dream home yours!
